Package com.camerontec.catalys.util.collection

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IClassInstanceFactory
    Factory for creating objects given a source of configuration data and also a registry for storing and accessing those object instances.
    IClassInstanceRegistry
    Registry (collection) of objects indexed by class and a String identifier.
    IFifoFileQueue
    FIFO file based queue interface.
    ResettableListIterator<E>
    Implementation of ResettableListIterator supporting Generics.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractClassInstanceFactory
    This class provides a skeletal implementation of the IClassInstanceFactory interface, to minimize the effort required to implement this interface.
    ClassInstanceRegistry
    Standard implementation of IClassInstanceRegistry.
    CleanerUtils  
    FifoFileQueue
    FIFO file queue implementation.
    IFifoFileQueue.Entry
    A single FIFO file queue entry.
    LinkedListWithResettableIterators<E>
    Standard Java LinkedList extended so that its LinkedListWithResettableIterators.listIterator() methods return ResettableListIterator 's.
    ListIteratorChain<E>
    Implemented as a wrapper on top of the multiple ResettableListIterators.
    NonDestructiveSetUtils
    Utilities for common set operations.
    OrderedRegistry<T>
    Simple registry implementation which contains named elements and ensures that iteration order is the same as insertion order.
    ResettableListIteratorFromList<E>
    Create a ResettableListIterator from any List.
    SmallIntMap
    Map optimized for small positive integer keys.
    SmallIntSet
    Set optimized for storing small positive integers.
